    <summaries>
      <summary>
        <versionCode>00</versionCode>
        <actionDate>2021-03-11</actionDate>
        <actionDesc>Introduced in Senate</actionDesc>
        <updateDate>2021-05-24T16:23:05Z</updateDate>
        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>NEPA Data Transparency and Accountability Act</b></p> <p>This bill requires federal agencies to annually report on their environmental review activities under the National Environmental Policy Act of 1969 (NEPA).</p> <p>The agencies must also include the cost of their NEPA activities in the annual reports after the Council on Environmental Quality and the Office of Management and Budget have developed a methodology to assess the comprehensive costs of the NEPA process.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
